HEADWORD: Potsdam group
<hw>Pots"dam group`</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>. <fld>(Geol.)</fld> <def>A
subdivision of the Primordial or Cambrian period in American geology; --
so named from the sandstone of <etsep>Potsdam</etsep>, New York. See
<xex>Chart</xex> of <er>Geology</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

